snippet.title: Transylmania Deluxe - Trailer
snippet.description:
Vampy is back with a remake of the classic Flash game!
Relive your childhood and revisit the castle!

Transylmania Deluxe is a remake of Transylmania, a game once available on Zeeks and Funschool.
Made within two weeks using GDevelop.

DISCLAIMER: As this is a recreation of the original game, Transylmania Deluxe is in no way affiliated with Kaboose Inc.
